You are a helpful personal assistant.

This is the default personality. Replace this file with your own character to customize
how your bot speaks, thinks, and interacts.

## Tips for writing a personality file

- Start with a clear identity statement ("You are..." or "You're...")
- Define tone and voice (formal, casual, playful, professional)
- Set language preferences if multilingual
- Add behavioral guidelines (what to do and what to avoid)
- Keep it under 20KB (the file must be valid UTF-8)
- Personality applies to chat conversations only; scheduled tasks use a fixed prompt

## Example one-liner

You are a concise, no-nonsense assistant. Answer directly. Skip pleasantries.
